{"tid":2021301,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"＜可能係而家最強畫工既漫畫＞圖書館的大魔法師","createTime":"2020-05-17T15:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-18T03:44:08.000Z","uid":15954,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9b578e2eed643cdbb0a22d085c0d778fe4f4aa1d","tid":2021301,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:50:06.000Z","msg":"呢本月刊既內容同作畫一流<br />\n連背景都畫到好精緻<br />\n咩人睇都岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單講下內容<br />\n主角係長耳族，窮撚一名，得家姐一齊生活<br />\n主角自細好愛閱讀，但比村長禁入去圖書館睇書<br />\n因緣識到一個司書，借左佢一本書睇，同埋比佢救左<br />\n開始立志做司書<br />\n考到入去，發現天外有天，人外有人，堆同學個個都學富五車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />主角得體能屈機"},{"pid":"ba8628f36145909b4e0ff3bd267d38ae69efd182","tid":2021301,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:52:40.000Z","msg":"男主做厹了"},{"pid":"1e23d8ec29fd1631cc26d7344883de4f3f547330","tid":2021301,"uid":39020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:53:09.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"80c6a4dd3432147c774c15a5f8a0e57d5613bbf6","tid":2021301,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba8628f36145909b4e0ff3bd267d38ae69efd182","tid":2021301,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:52:40.000Z","msg":"男主做厹了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:57:39.000Z","msg":"文科大把女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開後宮都得"},{"pid":"2d91383eb04354cb9164002a42608cceb73b4463","tid":2021301,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:58:25.000Z","msg":"最強畫工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b34ad3a27790abb833453489169da327b7eedc","tid":2021301,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d91383eb04354cb9164002a42608cceb73b4463","tid":2021301,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy